text: The Kermadec scalyfin, Parma kermadecensis, is a damselfish of the genus Parma, found around New Zealand's Kermadec Islands around depths of between 3 and 20 m, over shallow rocky reef areas. Its maximum length recorded is 22 centimeters. ==References== ==Other websites== * Royal Society of NZ Kermadec scalyfin Category:Fish of the Pacific Ocean
title: Kermadec scalyfin
